    <p><strong>Sub-Zero/Wolf ecosystem note:</strong> When outdoor and indoor Wolf appliances need service, we frequently combine into single-visit dispatches. Diagnostic fee covers full home Wolf inventory check on a single $120 charge, parts and labor billed separately per repair.</p>
